headline: Wall Street boom boosts profits at Bank of America, Morgan Stanley
summary: Third quarter profits at Bank of America and Morgan Stanley surged 23% and 45%, respectively, as the banking giants became the latest to benefit from a Wall Street dealmaking boom.
